Name: ToledoVR
About the game: ToledoVR is a action/strategy game for the HTC Vive. Play as a god from the top and fight as a hero on the ground. Playable both in VR and on the PC simultaneously (local multiplayer). Map 1: Gametype: MOBA (Use waves of units to destroy towers and finally the enemy) Gamemodes: Singleplayer (vs AI), local multiplayer (1vs1) Map 2: Gametype: RTS (Erect buildings and command units in real time) Gamemodes: Singleplayer (vs AI), local multiplayer (1vs1), local coop (survival mode)
